    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rembrunir is a game made to be played with one hand, the triggers on the back of the controller are the attack and super attack buttons, you move with the directional buttons and the Y, X, A, B buttons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case you do not have controls, the buttons to play on the keyboard are: A,W,S,D,R,T and for the second player they are U,H,J,K,O,P. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Single player mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Multiplayer versus mode (offline).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• One hand gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Super moves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Eight characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Eight stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Eight endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NOTE:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains DLC however it is not necessary to purchase it to activate them, you can choose to finish the story mode 50 times to obtain the DLC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE GAME DOES NOT AND WILL NOT HAVE ONLINE FUNCTIONS, AT THE MOST IT CAN BE PLAYED WITH STEAM REMOTE PLAY TOGETHER</p>",
